      "span_text": "Onset of the secondary progesterone rise was arbitrarily calculated based on the following formula [mean concentration progesterone primary progesterone rise + 2 x standard deviation primary progesterone rise ] with at least 2 consecutive days of progesterone concentrations exceeding this value"
